OL,3,CMan shot dead by officers after
OL,4,Copening fire near White House
OL,6,FA man who opened fire near a White
OL,7,FHouse security checkpoint has been
OL,8,Fshot dead by officers, the US Secret
OL,9,FService said.
OL,11,FThe man was near Pennsylvania Avenue
OL,12,Fwhen he "pulled a weapon from his bag"
OL,13,Fand opened fire shortly after 6pm US
OL,14,Flocal time on Saturday, 11pm BST, the
OL,15,Flaw enforcement agency said in a
OL,16,Fstatement on X.
OL,18,FOfficers returned fire, and the
OL,19,Fsuspect was taken to the hospital,
OL,20,Fwhere he died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
