OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779606368
OL,3,CMan shot dead by officers after
OL,4,Copening fire near White House
OL,6,FThe suspect was identified as 21-year-
OL,7,Fold Nasire Best, according to a law
OL,8,Fenforcement official.
OL,10,FCourt records show Best was arrested
OL,11,Fin July 2025 after attempting to enter
OL,12,Fa White House checkpoint without
OL,13,Fauthorisation, ignoring officers'
OL,14,Fcommands to stop and claiming he was
OL,15,FJesus Christ.
OL,17,FA court order was issued banning him
OL,18,Ffrom the area before trial, but a
OL,19,Fwarrant was issued in August after he
OL,20,Freportedly failed to comply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
