FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779606368
OL,3,CMan shot dead by officers after
OL,4,Copening fire near White House
OL,6,FThis is the third time in the past
OL,7,Fmonth that shots have been fired near
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump, after
OL,9,Fincidents at the White House
OL,10,FCorrespondents' Dinner in April and
OL,11,Fnear the Washington Monument earlier
OL,12,Fin May.
OL,14,FA bystander was also struck on
OL,15,FSaturday, though police are unclear
OL,16,Fwhether they were hit by the suspect's
OL,17,Fbullets or those fired by officers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
