OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779606368
OL,3,CMan shot dead by officers after
OL,4,Copening fire near White House
OL,6,FThe Secret Service said none of its
OL,7,Fofficers was injured and that Trump,
OL,8,Fwho was at the White House at the
OL,9,Ftime, was not "impacted".
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FTrump originally planned to spend the
OL,17,Fweekend at his New Jersey golf club,
OL,18,Fbut changed his plans on Friday and
OL,19,Fstayed at the White House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
