OL,3,CMan shot dead by officers after
OL,4,Copening fire near White House
OL,6,FFBI Director Kash Patel said on social
OL,7,Fmedia that agency personnel were on
OL,8,Fthe scene and "we will update the
OL,9,Fpublic as we're able."
OL,11,FYellow crime scene tape and dozens of
OL,12,Forange evidence markers could be seen
OL,13,Fon the pavement just outside the White
OL,14,FHouse complex, along with medical
OL,15,Fequipment, including what appeared to
OL,16,Fbe surgical gloves and emergency
OL,17,Fmedical kits.
